/*
============================================================
 TELEOP CONTROL MAP
============================================================

GAMEPAD 1  (DRIVER)
------------------------------------------------------------
 Right Stick (Y)                    Drive Forward / Backward
 Left Stick (X)                     Strafe Left / Right
 Right Stick (X)                    Rotate (Turn)
 A Button                           High Speed Mode (0.95)
 B Button                           Low Speed Mode  (0.40)
 X Button                           Normal Speed Mode (0.70)
 Y Button                           Unused
 D-Pad Down                         Toggle Vision (on/off)
 D-Pad (Up, Left, Right)            Unused
 Right Trigger/Bumper               Unused
 Left Trigger/Bumper                Unused

------------------------------------------------------------
GAMEPAD 2  (OPERATOR)
------------------------------------------------------------
 D-Pad Up                           Switch to AUTO shooter mode
 D-Pad Down                         Switch to MANUAL shooter mode
 D-Pad Right                        Arm / Disarm auto-spin (AUTO mode only)
 D-Pad Left                         Unused

 A Button                           Long-range shooter preset (Manual)
 B Button                           Mid-range shooter preset  (Manual)
 Left Bumper                        Short-range shooter preset (Manual)
 X Button                           Stop shooter (Manual)
 Y Button                           Feed ring (fires only when shooter ready)

 Right Trigger                      Intake forward
 Left Trigger                       Stop intake
 Right Bumper                       Reverse intake

------------------------------------------------------------
AUTOMATIC LOGIC
------------------------------------------------------------
 - Shooter only spins in AUTO mode if armed (D-Pad Right).
 - Servo feed (Y) works only when flywheel is at target velocity.
 - LED Status:
       Off (BLACK)  -> Vision disabled
       Red          -> No or incorrect tag detected
       Yellow       -> Correct tag detected, not at speed / not armed
       Green        -> Correct tag detected, flywheel ready
       Flash Yellow -> Driver pressed Y too early
 - Alliance goal tag hardcoded via GOAL_TAG_ID (20 = blue, 24 = red)
 - Logging toggle via LOG_ENABLED boolean
============================================================
*/